(33814, 91296, 0, 1, '藏-(重錄版本)', '', '2011-03-18 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'A1 想在天空裡去尋找一個家  到底我該身處何方\r\n\r\n   Want to find a homeland in the sky, what on earth should I belong to?\r\n\r\n   黑夜只是結束的開始 (而我又該往哪裡逃)\r\n\r\n   The night was just a starting of an end(and where is my escape?)\r\n\r\nA2 想在海平面裡遊走  卻又像行屍走肉\r\n\r\n   Want to walk in the sea and soar, only to be a living dead\r\n   \r\n   是否 真的 盲目\r\n\r\n   Am I ~ Truly ~blind~ \r\n\r\nB1 空氣凝結著我無法呼吸 暴風告訴我該到這裡結束\r\n\r\n   The air clots that I can not breath, storm telling me here is the end\r\n\r\n   樹裡的鳥兒為我呼喊  風兒叫我聽她訴說\r\n\r\n   Birds cry from surrounding trees, wind, calling me to be heard \r\n\r\nC1 你要的那個她 (已不適他) 你要的那個我 (已不適我)\r\n\r\n   The one you want, (wasn''t the one)  For me you want (it wasn''t me)\r\n\r\nD1 不管你說甚麼 what you say 我都會去做i will go \r\n\r\n   我告訴你 i tell you 我願意犧牲 i will sacrafice\r\n\r\n   從現在 From now on 我不害怕 I am not afraid \r\n\r\n   伸出我的手stretch my hand 朝天空邁進 Forward to the sky\r\n\r\n   我要你看見我的世界 i wanna you will see my world  (我會看到妳的一切 i will see your world)\r\n\r\n   我不會逃跑 i won,t run away (i will stay here forever)\r\n', '', 323, '', '桃利煬', '桃利煬', '桃利煬', 'Ｅ = ＭｘＣ平方 ', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-03-18 01:35:22', '2013-10-07 17:18:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
